provisions.content:
An applicant for membership or participation shall pay the following admission fees to
the CSX:
1-Member shall pay 20,000,000 (twenty million) Riels for the membership of Securities
Market Operator, Securities Clearing and Settlement Facility Operator, and the Securities
Depository Operator.
2- Participant shall pay admission fees as the following:
a- Cash Settlement Agent: 5,000,000 (five million) Riels;
b-Securities Registrar: 2,000,000 (two million) Riels;
c-Securities Transfer Agent: 2,000,000 (two million) Riels;
d- Listed company is exempted from paying the admission fee.
